<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= copy.heroTitle %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f7fb;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 32px 0;
        }
        .email-card {
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 28px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
        }
        .email-hero {
            background: <%= budget.accentColor %>;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 36px 44px 32px;
        }
        .email-hero span.label {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 600;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .email-hero h1 {
            margin: 16px 0 8px;
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .email-hero p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 520px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 36px 44px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .email-body ul {
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .email-body li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 8px;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: <%= budget.accentColor %>;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.22);
        }
        .email-footer {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 26px 44px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #64748b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .email-card {
                margin: 0 16px;
            }
            .email-hero,
            .email-body,
            .email-footer {
                padding: 28px;
            }
            .email-hero h1 {
                font-size: 26px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <span style="display:none;color:transparent;height:0;max-height:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;">
        <%= copy.previewText %>
    </span>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-card">
            <div class="email-hero">
                <span class="label"><i>●</i> Alerta financeiro</span>
                <h1><%= copy.heroTitle %></h1>
                <p><%= copy.heroSubtitle %></p>
            </div>
            <div class="email-body">
                <p>Olá <strong><%= user.firstName %></strong>,</p>
                <p>
                    Detectamos uma atualização importante no orçamento da categoria
                    <strong><%= budget.categoryName %></strong>.
                </p>

                <%- await include('./partials/budgetAlertSummary', { budget, displayMode: 'email' }) %>

                <% if (insights && insights.length) { %>
                    <ul>
                        <% insights.forEach((insight) => { %>
                            <li><%= insight %></li>
                        <% }) %>
                    </ul>
                <% } %>

                <a class="cta-button" href="<%= links.accessUrl %>"><%= copy.ctaLabel %></a>

                <p style="margin-top: 28px; font-size: 13px;">
                    Link seguro válido até <strong><%= tokens.access.expiresAtLabel %></strong>.
                    Não compartilhe este endereço: ele é exclusivo da sua conta e leva diretamente ao módulo de orçamentos.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="email-footer">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 8px;"><strong><%= meta.organizationName %></strong></p>
                <p style="margin: 0;">
                    Você recebeu este alerta automático do módulo financeiro.
                    Caso não reconheça a operação, revise as permissões de acesso e entre em contato com o time responsável.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
